text: The content from IRM 4.2.4 dated October 1, 2003 is obsolete. This IRM is obsolesced because the information in this IRM has been incorporated into IRM 4.10.1, Overview of Examiner Responsibilities, and IRM 25.1.4, Administrative Joint Investigation, as reﬂected in the crosswalk below:
